ith deriving\nplasma variables from the photospheric magnetograms as well as other sources of\nerrors such as reduced resolution and instrument bias and noise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2017 14:14:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-05"}
