igma_1(A)/\\sigma_{k+1}(A)$, then $\\|\\widehat{A}_k-A\\|_F \\leq\n(1+O(\\epsilon))\\|A-A_k\\|_F$ with high probability, where\n$\\widehat{A}=\\frac{1}{N}\\sum_{i=1}^N{X_iX_i^\\top}$ is the sample covariance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2017 15:43:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 5 Nov 2017 16:15:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-07"}
